  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    CompareDataWindow
    Window handler for comparing crimes.
    ConfirmationWindow
    This class holds the information for windows that open after a certain user action has happened.
    CrimeViewButton
    CrimeViewButton is the button on DataPane for viewing a crime in more detail.
    DataPane
    DataPane is a JavaFX pane that displays the data from a CrimeData object in a graphical representation.
    DataPaneConstructor
    Constructs CrimeData objects to DataPane objects to be displayed
    DataViewWindow
    Base class for viewing data in a larger window.
    EnterIDController
    Controller class for fxml file enter-id.fxml
    GeocoderApi
    Class which takes an input address and Geocodes it to get the result in a Json string text.
    GeocoderApiTest
    Junit test for the class GeocoderApi
    GraphViewController
    Class which used the data provided by the GraphCreator class and creates and populates graphs using the GraphViewWindow.
    GraphViewWindow
    Class which creates the Window that pops up after clicking the View Graph Button.
    Main
    The Main class which runs the application through the SafePoint class.
    MainViewController
    Main FXML controller for main-view.fxml
    PoliceDataPane
    PoliceDataPane extends DataPane that displays the data from a PoliceData object in a graphical representation.
    PoliceDataWindow
    Handles in depth displaying of PoliceData objects as a separate window.
    ReportCrimeController
    FXML Control file for FXML attributes in report-crime-view
    ReportCrimeWindow
    Handles the window for when a user wants to report a crime
    SafePoint
    Handles the creation of the main GUI for SafePoint

    UserDataWindow
    Handles in depth displaying of UserData objects as a separate window.
